{"tid":1554377,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"認真討論,有咩工可以好得過/同督察打成平手?","createTime":"2019-09-09T02:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T00:52:29.000Z","uid":248578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1063ab2e1c4579b55d07743691da9614173115","tid":1554377,"uid":248578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"警務督察2019年起薪: 47K<br />\n當24歲入職,起薪47K<br />\n29歲升高級督察76K (未計房屋津貼萬幾,特高MPF)<br />\n究竟有咩工可以匹敵?<br />\n我先拋磚引玉<br />\n1. 其他紀律部隊督察(雖然除左消防外,其他主任級無得考個試就升高級督察,但總算差唔多)<br />\n2. 醫生 (起薪5萬幾6萬,10萬都係4-5年內既事)<br />\n3. AO/EO<br />\n4. 入到國際大行既律師(Trainee 45-50k, Newly Qualified 70-85k, 執業5年基本上100-130k, 普通中等local firm律師就算尻數,Trainee 20k Newly Qualified 先about 40k, 人地起薪都未到)<br />\n5. iBanker (呢個唔使講)<br />\n<br />\n其實諗諗下,督察人工福利真係好撚屈機,唔怪得而家咁既時勢仲咁多人仆入去做<br />\n唯一比較明顯既缺點就係頭幾年大機會要輪班,始於比五日白領工辛苦<br />\n究竟仲有咩私人工拍得住督察?我諗真MT都好難?"},{"pid":"1937011fa7e2877d19418316deb2e0aa2113161f","tid":1554377,"uid":64153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"得人工高有鬼用<br />\n成班智商低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab595cb54abc383bef84e33f7ba9c5bb59d60276","tid":1554377,"uid":248578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1937011fa7e2877d19418316deb2e0aa2113161f","tid":1554377,"uid":64153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"得人工高有鬼用<br />\n成班智商低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"最令人心傷就係我讀咁撚多書都未有佢地起薪咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea8a404fb38fbcf93bd342e2b90c68e3